843
01:02:28,445 --> 01:02:30,863
because you thought I
was cheating on you.

844
01:02:30,864 --> 01:02:33,031
I don't like the idea,

845
01:02:33,032 --> 01:02:37,244
but I'm willing to, I don't know,

846
01:02:37,245 --> 01:02:42,791
