order to save our child.

847
01:02:42,792 --> 01:02:44,209
Your sacrifice?

848
01:02:44,210 --> 01:02:45,711
I hate this woman.

849
01:02:45,712 --> 01:02:47,880
We cannot let her kill our baby.

850
01:02:47,881 --> 01:02:49,381
