903
01:08:56,466 --> 01:08:58,167
And this is Tony.

904
01:08:58,168 --> 01:08:59,685
Heard so much about you, Katherine.

905
01:08:59,686 --> 01:09:03,922
KATE: One day her dad leaves
her alone with this friend

906
01:09:03,923 --> 01:09:06,508
