to have sex with him.

907
01:09:07,009 --> 01:09:10,595
- No, Tony stop.
- So he rapes her.

908
01:09:10,596 --> 01:09:14,933
Yeah, he rapes her.

909
01:09:14,934 --> 01:09:16,810
Good girl.

910
01:09:16,811 --> 01:09:18,880
