944
01:11:09,757 --> 01:11:12,550
In the end, she wins.

945
01:11:12,551 --> 01:11:15,887
Big.

946
01:11:15,888 --> 01:11:21,135
That, Mr. Kelly, is a great story.

947
01:11:22,812 --> 01:11:25,806
