helps me get through this.

950
01:12:38,012 --> 01:12:40,138
"I think of you every
waking moment,

951
01:12:40,139 --> 01:12:43,475
"and I can't wait
until this is over.

952
01:12:43,476 --> 01:12:46,227
"I adore you so much,

953
01:12:46,228 --> 01:12:51,232
